{
  "name": "TestJob",
  "type": "USql",
  "degreeOfParallelism": 1,
  "priority": 1000,
  "properties": {
    "type": "USql",
    "script": "	DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS onesdk1020; CREATE DATABASE onesdk1020;
	CREATE TABLE onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk4552
	(
			//Define schema of table
			UserId          int, 
			Start           DateTime, 
			Region          string, 
			Query           string, 
			Duration        int, 
			Urls            string, 
			ClickedUrls     string,
		INDEX idx1 //Name of index
		CLUSTERED (Region ASC) //Column to cluster by
		PARTITIONED BY (UserId) HASH (Region) //Column to partition by
	);
	ALTER TABLE onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk4552 ADD IF NOT EXISTS PARTITION (1);
	DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk1746;

	//create table weblogs on space-delimited website log data
	CREATE FUNCTION onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk1746()
	RETURNS @result TABLE
	(
		s_date DateTime,
		s_time string,
		s_sitename string,
		cs_method string, 
		cs_uristem string,
		cs_uriquery string,
		s_port int,
		cs_username string, 
		c_ip string,
		cs_useragent string,
		cs_cookie string,
		cs_referer string, 
		cs_host string,
		sc_status int,
		sc_substatus int,
		sc_win32status int, 
		sc_bytes int,
		cs_bytes int,
		s_timetaken int
	)
	AS
	BEGIN

		@result = EXTRACT
			s_date DateTime,
			s_time string,
			s_sitename string,
			cs_method string,
			cs_uristem string,
			cs_uriquery string,
			s_port int,
			cs_username string,
			c_ip string,
			cs_useragent string,
			cs_cookie string,
			cs_referer string,
			cs_host string,
			sc_status int,
			sc_substatus int,
			sc_win32status int,
			sc_bytes int,
			cs_bytes int,
			s_timetaken int
		FROM @"/Samples/Data/WebLog.log"
		USING Extractors.Text(delimiter:' ');

	RETURN;
	END;
	CREATE VIEW onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk1080 
	AS 
		SELECT * FROM 
		(
			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
		) 
	AS 
	T(a, b);
	CREATE PROCEDURE onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk4908()
	AS BEGIN
	  CREATE VIEW onesdk1020.dbo.onesdk1080 
	  AS 
		SELECT * FROM 
		(
			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
		) 
	  AS 
	  T(a, b);
	END;"
  }
}
